node.text:
LET THE WISPS GUIDE YOU
Our fate lives within us… you only have to be brave enough to see it! In this epic, brand new limited-time event, Merida, Queen Elinor, King Fergus, Lord Macintosh, Lord MacGuffin and Lord Dingwall are coming to the Kingdom, standing their ground and destined for adventure!

Last, but not least… we’re also adding the Comfy Merida Costume from Ralph Breaks the Internet to the game, so that you can continue your Comfy Princesses collection! And remember, a princess doesn’t play with her haggis! 😉

Join us for our limited-time Brave Event TODAY! 💙

node.text:
What have we here? It looks like the Jungle Cruise has come to Disney Magic Kingdoms! 🐘🌴

May your park patrons enjoy a leisurely ride on a canopied steamer, piloted by a trusty skipper - an amazing adventure along the Nile awaits! 👀💦

Have you watched the new live-action Jungle Cruise movie, Kingdomers? If so, let us know what you thought!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Disney Magic Kingdoms on July 31, 2021. May be a cartoon of 3 people and text.

node.text:
We can go anywhere, and we can do anything - we've just gotta stick together! 👦 🧡 👧

The end of this update may be approaching, but the good times we share as a community will continue to live on! 😁

What's one thing you've really enjoyed about Luca, Kingdomers? We'd love to hear from you! 💬

node.text:
Hiya, Kingdomers! Did you know that August 12th is World Elephant Day? 🐘💖

We added a special treat to celebrate, which we think you'll find rather... relephant. 😉😜

Which of this month's goodies are YOU most excited to receive? Let us know! 👇

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Disney Magic Kingdoms on July 28, 2021. May be a cartoon of 1 person and text.

node.text:
"Hang on!" 🛵 💨

Let's welcome Ercole, and do our best to help Luca and his pals win against him in the race of a lifetime! 💛 💪

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Disney Magic Kingdoms on July 26, 2021. May be a cartoon of 2 people and text.

node.text:
Walking is just like swimming without fins, and also… there's no water! 😆 💦

Have you challenged yourself to try something new this summer, Kingdomers? If so, let us know how it's going! ✨

It's never too late to learn something new. 😊 🧡

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Disney Magic Kingdoms on July 25, 2021. May be a cartoon of text.

node.text:
Have you been enjoying the event so far, Kingdomers? Feeling like the big cat in town? 😉 ✨

Let us know what you've accomplished so far, and remember - the event ends July 31st, so there's still time to take part! 😻
